                <span class="slide__number"></span>
                <h2 class="slide__title">會員名錄與分會商業生態</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="stats-row">
                <div class="stats-box">
                    <div class="stats-box__number">30</div>
                    <div class="stats-box__label">位現任會員</div>
                    <div class="stats-box__sub">
                        <div class="stats-box__sub-num">10+</div>
                        <div class="stats-box__sub-label">產業類別</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="industry-grid">
                    <div class="industry-tag" onclick="openModal('餐飲')">
                        <div class="industry-tag__count">5</div>
                        <div class="industry-tag__name">餐飲業</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="industry-tag" onclick="openModal('金融保險')">
                        <div class="industry-tag__count">3</div>
                        <div class="industry-tag__name">金融保險</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="industry-tag" onclick="openModal('專業服務')">
                        <div class="industry-tag__count">5</div>
                        <div class="industry-tag__name">專業服務</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="industry-tag" onclick="openModal('製造工程')">
                        <div class="industry-tag__count">3</div>
                        <div class="industry-tag__name">製造/工程</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="industry-tag" onclick="openModal('零售')">
                        <div class="industry-tag__count">5</div>
                        <div class="industry-tag__name">零售百貨</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="industry-tag" onclick="openModal('公職')">
                        <div class="industry-tag__count">2</div>
                        <div class="industry-tag__name">公職/政治</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="industry-tag" onclick="openModal('科技')">
                        <div class="industry-tag__count">1</div>
                        <div class="industry-tag__name">科技業</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="industry-tag" onclick="openModal('媒體')">
                        <div class="industry-tag__count">2</div>
                        <div class="industry-tag__name">媒體影音</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="industry-tag" onclick="openModal('美容')">
                        <div class="industry-tag__count">1</div>
                        <div class="industry-tag__name">美容SPA</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="quick-btns">
                <button class="quick-btn" onclick="openModal('幹部')">
                    <span class="quick-btn__icon">👔</span>
                    <span>幹部團隊</span>
                </button>
                <button class="quick-btn" onclick="openModal('理監事')">
                    <span class="quick-btn__icon">⭐</span>
                    <span>理監事會</span>
                </button>
                <button class="quick-btn" onclick="openModal('會員')">
                    <span class="quick-btn__icon">👥</span>
                    <span>一般會員</span>
                </button>
                <button class="quick-btn" onclick="openModal('all')">
                    <span class="quick-btn__icon">📋</span>
                    <span>全部名單</span>
                </button>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section" style="margin-top: 24px;">
                <h3 class="info-section__title">名錄的價值與任務</h3>
                <ul class="info-list">
                    <li>讓新會友快速認識「這個分會有誰、會什麼」</li>
                    <li>提供商業媒合與合作時的查詢工具</li>
                    <li>商業交流委員會任務：持續更新維護，讓名錄從「紙上資訊」變成「真正合作」</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== Slide 2: 商業交流委員會介紹 ========== -->
    <section class="slide slide--content">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <div class="slide__header">
                <span class="slide__number">01</span>
                <h2 class="slide__title">商業交流委員會是做什麼的？</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="quote-box">
                「把人脈、舞台、資源串起來，讓會友真的有商機。」
            </div>

            <div class="card-grid">
                <div class="card card--center">
                    <div class="card__icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" /><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" /><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87" /><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="card__title">幫會友賺到【人脈】</h3>
                    <p class="card__desc">讓會員之間互相認識、理解彼此的專業與需求，把「認識」變成「合作」</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card card--center">
                    <div class="card__icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" /><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="card__title">幫會友創造【舞台】</h3>
                    <p class="card__desc">提供上台分享、擺攤、展示產品服務的機會，用低風險方式試水溫</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card card--center">
                    <div class="card__icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" /><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12" /><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="card__title">幫分會建立【外部連結】</h3>
                    <p class="card__desc">對接政府單位、商圈、姐妹會，讓活動變成真正的商務與資源交流</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="tag-list">
                <span class="tag">👥 會友</span>
                <span class="tag">🏪 在地店家</span>
                <span class="tag">🏛️ 政府單位</span>
                <span class="tag">🤝 姐妹會</span>
                <span class="tag">🌐 合作夥伴</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== Slide 3: 價值說明 ========== -->
    <section class="slide slide--content">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <div class="slide__header">
                <span class="slide__number">02</span>
                <h2 class="slide__title">商業交流的價值：對誰有幫助？</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="card-grid">
                <div class="card card--center">
                    <div class="card__icon" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #60a5fa, #3b82f6);">
