                    <div class="card__icon" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4ade80, #22c55e);">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z" /><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="card__title">對分會</h3>
                    <p class="card__desc">打造「懂商業、會交流」的分會形象<br>活動有內容、有專業、也有溫度</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card card--center">
                    <div class="card__icon" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa, #8b5cf6);">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z" /><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="card__title">對地方與政府</h3>
                    <p class="card__desc">串連商圈與青年創業者<br>承接青年局等單位的政策與資源</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

