        <div class="slide-inner">
            <div class="slide__header">
                <span class="slide__number">03</span>
                <h2 class="slide__title">2026 商業交流委員會四大工作目標</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="card-grid card-grid--2">
                <div class="goal-card">
                    <div class="goal-card__num">1</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="goal-card__title">人脈連結</h3>
                        <p class="goal-card__desc">讓新舊會友都能彼此認識、熟悉專業</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="goal-card">
                    <div class="goal-card__num">2</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="goal-card__title">商機促成</h3>
                        <p class="goal-card__desc">讓介紹合作、接案、共創專案變成常態</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="goal-card">
                    <div class="goal-card__num">3</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="goal-card__title">學習成長</h3>
                        <p class="goal-card__desc">讓會友在品牌、行銷、AI 等面向一起升級</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="goal-card">
                    <div class="goal-card__num">4</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="goal-card__title">在地與國際連結</h3>
                        <p class="goal-card__desc">串聯商圈、政府與姐妹會，拓展新舞台</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== Slide 5: 目標一 - 人脈連結 ========== -->
    <section class="slide slide--content">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <div class="slide__header">
                <span class="slide__number">04</span>
                <h2 class="slide__title">目標一：人脈連結</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <h3 class="info-section__title">年度活動規劃</h3>
                <ul class="info-list">
                    <li>每年規劃 3–4 場交流活動（實體或線上）</li>
                    <li>商業小聚、Speed Networking、親子商業學習遊戲</li>
                    <li>讓會友在輕鬆氛圍中建立深度連結</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <h3 class="info-section__title">新會員融入機制</h3>
                <ul class="info-list">
                    <li>新會員三個月內至少有一次「舞台」機會</li>
                    <li>被介紹或自我介紹，讓大家認識你</li>
                    <li>協助建立個人簡介＋事業簡介</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== Slide 6: 目標二 - 商機促成 ========== -->
    <section class="slide slide--content">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <div class="slide__header">
                <span class="slide__number">05</span>
                <h2 class="slide__title">目標二：商機促成</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <h3 class="info-section__title">建立「會員事業名冊」</h3>
                <ul class="info-list">
                    <li>基本資料、產業別、服務內容</li>
                    <li>目前需求（找客戶？找合作？找供應商？）</li>
                    <li>每季整理 3–5 件實際合作或媒合案例</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <h3 class="info-section__title">活動設計巧思</h3>
                <ul class="info-list">
                    <li>名片交流時間(Speed Networking)／主題分組</li>
                    <li>需求留言牆：讓「我在找⋯」被看見</li>
                    <li>讓「認識」更容易變成「合作」</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== Slide 7: 目標三 - 學習成長 ========== -->
    <section class="slide slide--content">
        <div class="slide-inner">
            <div class="slide__header">
                <span class="slide__number">06</span>
                <h2 class="slide__title">目標三：學習成長</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <h3 class="info-section__title">主題學習活動（每年至少 2 場）</h3>
