                <h2 class="slide__title">給未來商業交流主委的三個問題</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="card-grid">
                <div class="q-card">
                    <div class="q-card__num">1</div>
                    <h4 class="q-card__title">今年最想幫會友解決的「痛點」是什麼？</h4>
